# Backend Rules (master-server)

## Stack
- Java 21, Spring Boot 3.5, Spring AI 1.1, Gradle
- PostgreSQL 17, OpenSearch 2.19, Lombok

## Patterns
- Use Lombok: @Data, @Builder, @Getter, @Setter, @AllArgsConstructor, @NoArgsConstructor
- Controllers: @RestController, map to /api/*
- Services: @Service, inject via constructor (Lombok @RequiredArgsConstructor)
- Config: @Configuration + @ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "...")
- DTOs: prefer Java records for immutable data
- LLM interaction: use Spring AI ChatClient and Advisor APIs
- Model routing: configured per-operation in application.yml under game-master.routing.operations

## Prompt Templates
- Location: src/main/resources/prompts/*.txt
- Syntax: {variableName} placeholders
- Always request JSON output with explicit schema for structured responses
- Prompts are multilingual (default Catalan, configurable)

## Configuration
- Centralized in application.yml
- Semantic prefixes: game-master.*, whisper.*, piper-tts.*, tts.*, audio.*, adventure.*
- Docker Compose auto-starts with Spring Boot

## Security
- Never hardcode API keys; use env vars: OPENAI_API_KEY, GOOGLE_GENAI_API_KEY, GM-PROJECT
